    "title": "The Mean-Field Equations for the Euclidean Gas",
    "nl_statement": "The evolution of the Euclidean Gas in the mean-field limit is described by a coupled system for the alive density $f(t,z)$ and the dead mass $m_d(t)$, involving kinetic transport, interior killing, revival, and internal cloning operators.",
